Text: RE GISB Base ContractI have filled in all of the necessary information under the contract but would like to request that under Section the Transaction Procedure Type be Written rather than Oral Please let me know if this is not possible Also you have indicated that Seller will be responsible for initiating the Transaction Confirmation When will Prairielands be receiving the Confirmation for the term deal done by Paul Lucci for the time period of through Let me know if you need any further information from me Please send out two originals to my attention at the address noted on the contract and I will return on fullyexecuted copy to your attention Thank you and talk to you soon Nancy K Senger Contract Lease Administrator Original Message From SMTP Sent Wednesday November AM To Subject Re GISB Base Contract Further to our conversation here is the GISB draft for your review See attached file Prairie Lands GISBdoc Regards Debra Perlingiere Enron North America Corp Legal Department Smith Street EB Houston Texas Phone Fax File Prairie Lands GISBdoc
